name: hanfei1986/Oversampling-of-imbalanced-data-with-RandomOverSampler-SMOTE-and-ADASYN
description: Imbalanced data commonly exist in real world, especially in anomaly-detection tasks. Handling imbalanced data is important to the tasks, otherwise the predictions are biased towards the majority class. RandomOverSampler, SMOTE, and ADASYN are useful oversampling tools to fabricate data for minority classes and make the dataset balanced.
